{{define "subject"}}Welcome to GradConnect — Please Verify Your Email{{end}}

{{define "plainBody"}}
Hi {{.FirstName}},

Welcome to GradConnect! We're excited to help you navigate your graduate career journey.

To get started, please verify your email address by clicking the link below:

https://gradconnect.com/verify?token={{.ActivationToken}}

If you didn't create an account with us, please ignore this email.

Best regards,
The GradConnect Team
{{end}}

